==English==

===Pronunciation===
ther-mo-karst'
===Noun===
'''Thermokarst'''
#{{geology}} A region similar in appearance to [[karst]] [[topography]], characterized by an irregular land surface, with [[bogs]], [[pits]], and other [[depressions]], formed in areas of [[permafrost]] due to ice melting.
